I-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-MsNpWiZ6w7j6lhO7O5gYyg">Mạn hứng (II) kỳ 3 - 漫興其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-C%E1%BB%91c/Nh%E1%BA%A1n/poem-bscCxIHhVA0MyNadMMRQIw">Nhạn - 雁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-C%E1%BB%91c/author-dSnmLveHQYvLVD8-n4k18A">Trịnh Cốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Thu-thanh-ph%C3%BA/poem-8gcYBavPuRIW4ppkAryC9g">Thu thanh phú - 秋聲賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%A5c/Ti%E1%BB%85n-Tri%E1%BB%81u-Ti%C3%AAn-qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%A9-Du%E1%BA%ABn-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Th%C4%83ng-L%C3%BD-Tr%C3%AD-Trung/poem-W7wWxNmcmKRZI4anGk7bsQ">Tiễn Triều Tiên quốc sứ Duẫn Đông Thăng, Lý Trí Trung - 餞朝鮮國使尹東昇，李致中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%A5c/author-jqgnFDAZWR6nfZEs-kEskQ">Đoàn Nguyễn Thục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-AGKUOTf4MNBoRtTrY2zw2A">Trần tình biểu - 陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/author-2WZpsdSFEWvTQerf8uTifQ">Lý Mật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%B1-kinh-ph%C3%B3-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-Ti%C3%AAn-huy%E1%BB%87n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C5%A9-b%C3%A1ch-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-qHlDll4qtUH2nCJy2-kR4Q">Tự kinh phó Phụng Tiên huyện vịnh hoài ngũ bách tự - 自京赴奉先縣詠懷五百字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
